query:
SELECT p.id, p.name, p.categoryId, c.name as category_name
FROM products p
LEFT JOIN categories c ON p.categoryId = c.id
WHERE p.name LIKE '%Rat Guardian%' 
   OR p.name LIKE '%Ox Guardian%'
   OR p.name LIKE '%Tiger Guardian%'
   OR p.name LIKE '%Rabbit Guardian%'
   OR p.name LIKE '%Dragon Guardian%'
   OR p.name LIKE '%Snake Guardian%'
LIMIT 10;
